data.description: Check out this expansive three-bungalow nestled in Wyandotte! Its fantastic layout boasts hardwood floors and original wood trim throughout. On the main level, you'll find two cozy bedrooms, a full bath, and a spacious living room flooded with natural light, complete with a built-in hutch. The dining area seamlessly transitions into the beautifully updated kitchen. Upstairs, the bedroom welcomes you with inviting hardwood paneling and flooring, featuring built-in dressers and recessed shelving with hidden storage closets! Enjoy the fenced backyard, a one-car detached garage, and peace of mind with newer roof and HVAC systems. Plus, all appliances are included in the sale.
